{
  "design_notes": "The chart is built around a high-tempo 184 BPM drive. Intro uses simple, steady steps on key beats to keep the player moving. S1 and S2 build up the intensity with light crossover movement and gradual introduction of streams. S3 features the primary drop where we introduce dense jumpstreams and zigzag movement patterns on eighth notes, keeping within the 8.0 NPS budget. Vocal sections in S4 and S7 are highlighted using sustain holds and rolls. The peaks of S5 and S6 are mapped with tight drills and accent jumps. The break fades out with quiet breathing steps.",
